         <div class="titoleto"><a name="d3e3872"> </a>Changing the number plate light bulb
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e3875"> </a>To reach the number plate light bulb (5), open the number plate lens (6), pull the bulb out of the holder and replace it.
         </div>
      </div>
